faultinject is a library designed to stress test applications. It is designed
to return errors from standard system library calls. The project was
developed by WiredTiger.

The general project layout is based on the jemalloc project.

The COPYING file contains copyright and licensing information.

The INSTALL file contains information on how to configure, build, and install
faultinject.

The ChangeLog file contains a brief summary of changes for each release.

URL: http://www.wiredtiger.com
